				Looking to connect with professionals in Strategy, Human Capital, Digital Transformation, and Risk Advisory who believe the future of work must be both data-intelligent and human-first.
			</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20">
				Start a Conversation
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
